snippet.title: Arcade Game: Sky Diver (1978 Atari)
snippet.description: Sky Diver is a two-player action game. By opening your parachute, jumping from a plane, and guiding your skydiver safely to a landing pad, you want to get the most points possible. If you wait too long to open your parachute, it won't open at all, and you won't get as many points for a successful landing. Your skydiver will be blown off course by varying wind conditions at each jump. A breeze sock at the lower part of the screen will assist you with deciding the breeze speed and bearing so you can redress. The player with the most points at the end of the nine jumps wins.
